                    "text": "For an ex and let be the segment ation result with the ample, \u2018.\u2019, \u2018/\u2019, \u2018:\u2019, \u2018%\u2019 and \u2018\\\u2019 are usually recog maximum likelihood.",
                    "sid": 56,
