                },
                {
                    "text": "2.3 Confidence measure and post process-.",
                    "sid": 65,
                    "ssid": 6,
                    "kind_of_tag": "s"
                },
                {
                    "text": "ing for final result There are two segmentation results for substrings with low MP candidates after reprocessing using HMM.",
                    "sid": 66,
                    "ssid": 7,
                    "kind_of_tag": "s"
                },
                {
                    "text": "Analyzing experiments data, we find wrong tags labeled by CRF are mainly: OOV words in test data, IV words and incorrect words recognized by CRF.",
                    "sid": 67,
                    "ssid": 8,
                    "kind_of_tag": "s"
                },
                {
                    "text": "Rectifying the tags with lower MP simply may produce an even worse performance in some case.",
                    "sid": 68,
                    "ssid": 9,
                    "kind_of_tag": "s"
                },
                {
                    "text": "For example, some OOV words are recognized correctly by CRF but with low MP.",
                    "sid": 69,
                    "ssid": 10,
                    "kind_of_tag": "s"
                },
                {
                    "text": "So, we can\u2019t accept the revised results completely.",
                    "sid": 70,
                    "ssid": 11,
                    "kind_of_tag": "s"
                },
                {
