                {
                    "text": "3.1 Closed.",
                    "sid": 74,
                    "ssid": 15,
                    "kind_of_tag": "s"
                },
                {
                    "text": "test The rule for the closed test in Bakeoff is that no additional information beyond training corpora is allowed.",
                    "sid": 75,
                    "ssid": 16,
                    "kind_of_tag": "s"
                },
                {
                    "text": "Following the rule, the closed test is designed to compare our system with other CWS systems.",
                    "sid": 76,
                    "ssid": 17,
                    "kind_of_tag": "s"
                },
                {
                    "text": "Five metrics of SIGHAN Bakeoff are used to evaluate the segmentation results: F-score (F), recall (R), precision (P), the recall on IV words (RIV) and the recall on OOV words (Roov).",
