                },
                {
                    "text": "Comparison our closed results with the top three in all test sets Next, we compare it with other top three systems.",
                    "sid": 145,
                    "ssid": 86,
                    "kind_of_tag": "s"
                },
                {
                    "text": "From the table 3 we can see that our system achieves better performance on closed test.",
                    "sid": 146,
                    "ssid": 87,
                    "kind_of_tag": "s"
                },
                {
                    "text": "In contrast, the values of RIV of our method are superior to others\u2019, which contributes to the model we use.",
                    "sid": 147,
                    "ssid": 88,
                    "kind_of_tag": "s"
                },
                {
                    "text": "Whether the features of AV for character-based CRF tagger or HMM revising, they all make good use of word information of training corpora.",
                    "sid": 148,
                    "ssid": 89,
                    "kind_of_tag": "s"
                },
                {
                    "text": "3.2 Open test.",
                    "sid": 149,
                    "ssid": 90,
                    "kind_of_tag": "s"
                },
                {
                    "text": "In the open test, the only additional source we use is the dictionary mentioned above.",
                    "sid": 150,
                    "ssid": 91,
                    "kind_of_tag": "s"
                },
                {
                    "text": "We get one first and two third best.",
                    "sid": 151,
                    "ssid": 92,
                    "kind_of_tag": "s"
                },
                {
                    "text": "Our result is showed in table 4.",
                    "sid": 152,
                    "ssid": 93,
                    "kind_of_tag": "s"
                },
                {
                    "text": "Compared with closed test, the value of RIV is increased in all test corpora.",
                    "sid": 153,
                    "ssid": 94,
                    "kind_of_tag": "s"
                },
                {
                    "text": "But we only get the higher value of F in domain of literature.",
                    "sid": 154,
                    "ssid": 95,
                    "kind_of_tag": "s"
                },
                {
                    "text": "The reasons will be analyzed as follows: In the open test, the OOV words are split into pieces because our model may be more dependent on the dictionary information.",
                    "sid": 155,
                    "ssid": 96,
                    "kind_of_tag": "s"
                },
                {
                    "text": "Consequently, we get higher value of R but lower P. The training corpora are the same as closed test, but it is different that FRE features are added.",
                    "sid": 156,
                    "ssid": 97,
                    "kind_of_tag": "s"
                },
                {
                    "text": "The additional features enhance the original information of IV words, so the value of RIV is improved to some extent.",
                    "sid": 157,
                    "ssid": 98,
                    "kind_of_tag": "s"
                },
                {
                    "text": "However, they have side effects for OOV segmentation.",
                    "sid": 158,
                    "ssid": 99,
                    "kind_of_tag": "s"
                },
                {
                    "text": "We will continue to solve this problem in the future work.",
                    "sid": 159,
                    "ssid": 100,
                    "kind_of_tag": "s"
                },
